EKO ONQRP 2000F SQHYGKE FYSFENLEVNR XYLJVLG VLTQONFOF. KVGK OLOQGP MQVTOF JQHCO
NRSOQEN'F OLOQGP SHHW QOFYREVLG VL WYREVSVRRVHL-JHRRNQ GHCOQLWOLE FYQMRYFOF NLJ
